parameters:
\n<sine:ω>ω: Hmph, I never expected it to come to this. But,
too bad for you!

\n<sine:ω>ω: This door has multiple layers of security, so
it won't open with a simple analysis!

\n<sine:ω>ω: Kishishi! While you were leisurely analyzing,
I've gathered all the drones in the entire floor!
\n<sine:ω>ω: Why... is the door... c...coming here!!

\n<Detective>Why did the door open by itself...? Well, never
mind. Let's chase after it for now.

\n<sine:ω>ω: *panting* Why is the lock... acting strange...
the system should be functioning properly...

\n<Detective>...Well, could you please open it quickly? Once I
ask what I want to ask, it's a different story...

\n<sine:ω>ω: Shut up! I absolutely won't forgive you
anymore!

\n<sine:ω>ω: I'm going to expose your perverted actions to
the whole world on today's live broadcast!

\n<sine:ω>ω: Kishishi! This should do it! I've double-locked
it, so there's no way you can get in! Take that,
you damn old fart!

\n<sine:ω>Why... even here... the system is functioning
normally... Could it be... perhaps...

\n<Detective>...Well, it seems like it's over. Accept your
fate.

\n<sine:ω>ω: You have quite the relaxed attitude to lecture
someone like me! That's fine by me! If that's how
it is, I'll take you on seriously!

\n<sine:ω>ω: Who do you think I am? I am the genius gamer
and genius hacker, none other than \c[2]Cocoa-
sama\c[0], also known as sine:ω!

\n<sine:ω>ω: This drone is a \c[2]special creation\c[0] that
I meticulously designed! Don't think it's the same
as any other drone up until now!
\n<Detective>(Damn it... What's this!? My heart is racing...)

\n<Detective>...Since you've provoked me so much... I assume
you're prepared, right...?
Do you want to see Cocoa's defeat scene?
▼戦闘勝利、エロシーン後イベント▼
ココ\SE[cry]\n<sine:ω>ω: Ugh... I can't get married anymore...
\n<Detective>I'm sorry, did I go a little too far?

ココ\SE[tere]\n<sine:ω>ω: ...Well... it's actually my fault for using the
gas... so it's not a big deal...

\n<Detective>...Ah, can you tell me more about that gas and the
phenomenon of \c[2]madness\c[0]?
ココ\SE[cry]わ…分かった…。\!狂人化について詳しい原理は知らないけど…あのガスの素は\c[2]ルナ姉\c[0]\n<sine:ω>ω: I received it...

ココ\SE[cry]\n<sine:ω>ω: There's no doubt that Luna-neechan is the
mastermind behind everything.

ココ\SE[cry]ゲームだって聞いたからボクも乗ったけど、\c[2]ボクの反則行為\c[0]\n<sine:ω>ω: Looking at the place where I wasn't forgiven...
this is the game board controlled by Luna-neechan.

ココ\SE[cry]\c[2]この先にいる奴ら\c[0]\n<sine:ω>ω: Including everything, it's a game that is set
on the rails laid by Luna-neechan. That's all I
know.
\n<Detective>The game... the rules... both you and that girl...

ココ\SE[cry]\n<sine:ω>ω: Just so you know, I don't know anything else. I
didn't like being bound by rules made by others,
so I did some probing...

sine:ω quickly took out a keyboard and started
typing something.

ココ\SE[cry]狂人化現象は、\c[2]朔晦(タチゴリ)市\c[0]\n<sine:ω>ω: It's occurring frequently in the area. The
police have surely investigated this, right?

\n<Detective>Ah, that's why investigators, including myself,
have been dispatched intensively to this area.

ココ\SE[cry]それで、現象が起き始めた時期にこの近辺で起きた他の事象がないか調べたの。\!そしたら、ある時期から色んな企業や団体がこの近辺の\c[2]都市開発事業\c[0]\n<sine:ω>ω: I found out that he had made a large
investment...

ココ\SE[cry]\n<sine:ω>ω: Development was once widely covered by the
media and reported as a great success, but now the
town is in a depopulated state. The period of
decline coincided with the occurrence of the
phenomenon.

\n<Detective>Why did the business decline...? Are there reasons
other than the phenomenon?
ココ\SE[tere]\n<sine:ω>ω: Um... huh? The firewall here is quite thick...

ココ\SE[default]\n<sine:ω>ω: Kishishi! Your little tricks won't work on
me...tto!

ココ\SE[default]\n<sine:ω>ω: ...Look, there are photos of the anti-eviction
protesters holding banners during the construction
phase, and photos of protest demonstrations!

ココ\SE[default]\n<sine:ω>ω: These two in the photo look suspicious, don't
they? It's like they silenced the opposition,
right?

An elderly man and a tough-looking man with a
large family crest on their backs are standing
side by side...

\n<Detective>This family crest... \c[2]Kurube\c[0]... The
\c[2]Kurube Group\c[0], a designated organized
crime syndicate... To think they would come here
and bring violence...

ココ\SE[default]\n<sine:ω>ω: To accomplish such a large-scale business in
such a short period of time, they must have used
not only a significant amount of funds, but also
some forceful methods! Look, not just in Japan...
umm? Rusukaya...?

ココ\SE[default]\n<sine:ω>ω: Huh?! But we were just getting to a good
part...

\n<Detective>It's dangerous to go any further. No matter how
confident you are in your abilities, there are
things in this world that you should never touch.

\n<Detective>(...If that's the case, they must have done
something significant... And that something is the
cause of the phenomenon of madness...)

\n<Detective>Is it possible to list the companies and
organizations involved based on the scope of the
investigation so far?
ココ\SE[cry]\n<sine:ω>ω: I can do something like that... Here you go.

\n<Detective>...Thank you. You have talent, so stop engaging in
dangerous games and use your abilities properly.
ココ\SE[tere]\n<sine:ω>ω: Ah... Of course! Wh... Who do you think I am...

\n<Detective>It's a promise. If you ever feel like you're
getting involved in something or if you have any
trouble, contact me. Here, this is my phone
number...

ココ\SE[default]\n<sine:ω>ω: ...Pfft...Kishishi...Who uses phones these
days? LOL
\n<Detective>...If you don't need it, then it's fine.

ココ\SE[default]\n<sine:ω>ω: Hehe~ Don't underestimate the genius me! I can
remember anything I see, even for a moment! I'll
prank call you every day, just you wait!

ココ\SE[tere]\n<sine:ω>ω: Kishi...eh...hehe....then, then I'll open the
door...!

\n<sine:ω>ω: Ah! I almost forgot to mention! Be careful not
to hurt your head in the next stage, \c[2].
\n<Detective>Huh? Ah...alright, I'll keep that in mind.

\n<sine:ω>ω: Mmm... I wonder if it'll be okay... It would be
nice if I can escape \c[2] properly... \c[0].
